data.enText: a type of glue used for sticking light things together, such as paper
a firm transparent fruit-flavoured sweet/candy that you chew
to spread glue on the surface of sth; to stick two things together with glue

data.chText: 包装袋上贴上了一大张地址签条。

gummed labels (= with glue on one side)

means: 黏胶，胶质物(用以粘轻东西，如纸等)

data.enText: to cover or fill sth with a sticky substance so that it stops moving or working as it should

tr: the tissue (covered by mucous membrane) of the jaws that surrounds the bases of the teeth
a preparation (usually made of sweetened chicle) for chewing
any of various trees of the genera Eucalyptus or Liquidambar or Nyssa that are sources of gum
wood or lumber from any of various gum trees especially the sweet gum
cement consisting of a sticky substance that is used as an adhesive
any of various substances (soluble in water) that exude from certain plants
they are gelatinous when moist but harden on drying

example: these trees gum in the Spring

tr: chew without teeth and with great difficulty
example: the old man had no teeth left and mumbled his food

tr: cover, fill, fix or smear with or as if with gum
example: if you gum the tape it is stronger

value.def: Gum is a substance, usually tasting of mint, which you chew for a long time but do not swallow.
Your gums are the areas of firm, pink flesh inside your mouth, which your teeth grow out of.

example.ex: The toothbrush gently removes plaque without damaging the gums.
example.tran: 这种牙刷可以温和去除牙菌斑而不损伤齿龈。

value.def: Gum is a type of glue that is used to stick two pieces of paper together.

example.ex: He was holding up a pound note that had been torn in half and stuck together with gum.
example.tran: 他举着一张被撕成两半后又用胶粘在一起的一英镑的钞票。

value.def: If two things are gummed together, they are stuck together.

example.ex: It is a mild infection in which a baby's eyelashes can become gummed together.
example.tran: 这是一种轻微感染，会导致婴儿睫毛粘在一起。

value.def: Gum is a sticky substance which comes from the eucalyptus tree or from various other trees and shrubs.

trans: 黄胞胶， 三仙胶 (使食物变稠的化学物质)
